b'Kamakura':
b'"A snow-covered house is situated in the middle of a rice field.
What should one do, in a space of white and quietude?
By spring, the snowy hut melts and loses its appearance.
The Japanese MA, the in-between state of time and space \xe2\x80\x93
an animation, a haiku"

(Source: Berlinale 2014 programme)'
